          "id": "cto_faq_5",
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What's your disaster recovery and uptime SLA?",
            "answer": "99.9% uptime SLA with automatic failover and redundant infrastructure across multiple availability zones. Full disaster recovery with RPO under 15 minutes and RTO under 1 hour. We maintain hot backups of all data and can restore to any point in the last 30 days. Your business stays running even when things go wrong."
          }
        }
